<section id="spotlight_character">
    <h1 id="hd_id31705511866295"><variable id="h1"><link href="text/swriter/01/SpotlightCharStyles.xhp">Spotlight Character Styles</link></variable></h1>
    <paragraph id="par_id481705511866297" role="paragraph">Activates spotlighting of character styles.</paragraph>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id881705514569887">Spotlighting character styles allows a better control of the application of character styles in the document.</paragraph>
<section id="howtoget">
    <embed href="text/swriter/00/00000405.xhp#spot_character"/>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id171705512039793">Character style spotlight displays the styled characters with a background color and a call-out with an unique number for each applied character style in the document. The background color and call-out number are also displayed in the corresponding character entry in the <menuitem>Styles</menuitem> deck on the sidebar.</paragraph>
<note id="par_id371705509091105">Character styles are not given a color and call-out number until they are applied in the document.</note>
<tip id="par_id21705518127906">When the extended tips features is enabled in <switchinline select="sys"><caseinline select="MAC"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools – Options</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> – LibreOffice – General</menuitem>, a tooltip shows the style name and many attributes of the style applied.</tip>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id811705512892082">Character direct formatting attributes are <link href="text/shared/01/05020100.xhp">Font</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05020200.xhp">Font Effects</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05020500.xhp">Position</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05020600.xhp">Asian Layout</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05020400.xhp">Hyperlink</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05210100.xhp">Highlighting</link> and <link href="text/shared/01/05030500.xhp">Borders</link>.  </paragraph>
<tip id="par_id791705511272699">Use the <link href="text/swriter/01/spotlight_chars_df.xhp">Spotlight Direct Character Formatting</link> command to display character direct formatting.</tip>
